         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Botanical Museum ¶ 10 September 1863. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honour to apply for six weeks leave of absence from the first of November next. ¶  ¶ You are aware that in consequence of your contemplated ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">63.09.10</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Carl Wilhelmi</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">C63/7429, unit 749, VPRS 1189/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanical Museum</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">10 September 1863.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honour to apply for six weeks leave of absence from the first of November next.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You are aware that in consequence of your contemplated visit to Europe I was precluded from applying last year for the three weeks leave under the 36 Clause of the Civil Service Act, and I therefore trust that you will feel justified in recommending the Honorable the Chief Secretary to accede to my present request, particularly as I have had never leave of absence during the eight years that I have had the honour to be in your department.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wilhelmi's letter<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">was enclosed with M to J. McCulloch, 11 September 1863 (in this edition as 63-09-11b)</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'for the favorable consideration of the honor. the Chief Secretary'. McCulloch minuted his approval<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">on</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M's covering letter on</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>18 September and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">this</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was forwarded to M on 23 September.</p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">Spotted potential ambiguity of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; color: #C00000; ">this</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">, depending where the information</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">of the reply to M comes.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">Perhaps should just say " …<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>18 September, and M was notified on 23 September"<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; "
                        xml:lang="en">There is a minute on 63-09-11b<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that is also potentially ambiguous, but approval was minuted on that covering<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>letter. So perhaps a similar formulation could be used there too?</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Carl Wilhelmi</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr. Ferd. Mueller F.R.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Director of the Botanic Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">&amp;c <space unit="chars" quantity="5"/>&amp;c <space unit="chars" quantity="5"/>&amp;c</p>
         </div>
